    "Our knowledgeable self-learning approach enhances trajectory quality through two key phases: (1) Filtering: We start by selecting correct trajectories, T correct, based on their outcomes.",
    "Specifically for task HotpotQA, we apply action knowledge to further refine these trajectories.",
    "This refinement involves removing any trajectories that do not align with the provided AK m, particularly those with invalid actions or disordered action sequences.",
    "(2) Merging: We then merge trajectories generated by models across different iterations.",
    "For trajectories addressing the same task, We refine them based on efficiency, specifically retaining the more efficient (shorter path) trajectories ensuring optimal problem-solving effectiveness."
